[Since the start of this reocurring epizootic of FMDV-O, 3 Dec 2014, a total of 121 outbreaks have been reported, including the above 41 new outbreaks. A map showing all 121 outbreaks is available at http://www.oie.int/wahis_2/public/wahid.php/Reviewreport/Review/viewsummary?fupser=&dothis=&reportid=16695. - Mod.AS

A HealthMap/ProMED-mail map can be accessed at: https://promedmail.org/promed-post?place=3260788,195.]
